\begin_layout Standard
\noindent
I am submitting my manuscript entitled 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

The Impact of El Nino-Southern Oscillation (ENSO) on Agricultural Stock
 Returns
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 for consideration for publication in Water Resources and Economics.
 The paper makes several contributions to the broader literature on the
 economic and financial effects weather fluctuations.
 First, the paper represents the first attempt to estimate and evaluate
 the effects of ENSO on U.S.
 agricultural stock returns.
 Second, unlike previous studies that use dummy variable measures to identify
 periods of ENSO and non-ENSO events, our econometric specification employs
 a continuous measure of ENSO intensity based on sea surface temperature
 anomalies (SSTA).
 Third, the dynamic effects of ENSO on agricultural stock returns are estimated
 using a structural vector autoregression (VAR) model.
 Fourth, we explore asymmetries in the effects of ENSO shocks by investigating
 the extent to which the responses of U.S.
 agricultural stock returns differ depending on whether the ENSO shocks
 are El Niño, La Niña, or neutral shocks.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $ $
\end_inset


\end_layout

